      "title": "Case class definitions.",
      "text": "\nimport scala.collection.mutable.ArrayBuffer\ncase class s3TQu(dimension:String,Degree:String,scalar:String,index:String,maxIndex:String,divisor:String,rowCounter:String)\ncase class s3TRe(dimension:String,Degree:String,scalar:String,index:String,maxIndex:String,divisor:String,rowCounter:String,result:String)\ncase class rResult(rowCounter:String,n:String, maxN:String,dim:String,rowResult:BigDecimal)\ncase class indexSum(iSum:String,finalISum:String)\ncase class consistant(rowCounter:BigDecimal,n:BigDecimal, maxN:String,dim:BigDecimal)\ncase class tupleQuippy(terms:ArrayBuffer[s3TQu],result:BigDecimal)",
